Create working dir and init git.
$ git init
$ git remote add â€“f origin https://github.com/lutzer/sahabe.git
$ git config core.sparsecheckout true
$ echo de.sahabe.backend_alter/src >> .git/info/sparse-checkout
$ echo de.sahabe.ui >> .git/info/sparse-checkout
$ git pull origin master
$ git push --set-upstream origin/master master
$ git pull

see also http://jasonkarns.com/blog/subdirectory-checkouts-with-git-sparse-checkout/
